{"text_id":172601,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Shift"," on"," a"," Cello","\n\n","Learning"," to"," shift"," on"," a"," cello"," is"," essential"," for"," advancing"," your"," playing"," skills"," and"," accessing"," a"," wider"," range"," of"," notes"," and"," musical"," expressions","."," Shifting"," enables"," you"," to"," move"," smoothly"," from"," one"," position"," to"," another"," on"," the"," cello","'","s"," finger","board","."," In"," this"," guide",","," we"," will"," walk"," you"," through"," the"," steps"," to"," master"," shifting"," with"," precision"," and"," confidence",".","\n\n","##"," ","1","."," Place"," your"," left"," hand"," in"," first"," position"," on"," any"," string",".","\n\n","Begin"," by"," positioning"," your"," left"," hand"," in"," the"," first"," position"," on"," any"," string","."," This"," position"," is"," where"," you"," typically"," start"," playing"," on"," the"," cello","."," Your"," thumb"," should"," rest"," gently"," on"," the"," back"," of"," the"," neck",","," and"," your"," fingers"," should"," hover"," above"," the"," strings",".","\n\n","##"," ","2","."," Lift"," your"," fingers"," up"," above"," the"," strings",".","\n\n","With"," your"," left"," hand"," in"," the"," first"," position",","," carefully"," lift"," your"," fingers"," slightly"," above"," the"," strings","."," Ensure"," that"," your"," fingers"," are"," relaxed"," and"," not"," pressing"," down"," too"," hard","."," This"," preparation"," will"," facilitate"," a"," smooth"," shifting"," motion",".","\n\n","##"," ","3","."," Move"," your"," hand"," slowly"," and"," smoothly"," towards"," one"," of"," the"," basic"," positions",".","\n\n","Slowly"," slide"," your"," left"," hand"," up"," the"," finger","board"," while"," maintaining"," a"," relaxed"," grip","."," Focus"," on"," making"," this"," movement"," smooth"," and"," controlled","."," It","'","s"," crucial"," to"," keep"," your"," thumb"," loose"," and"," allow"," it"," to"," glide"," along"," the"," neck",".","\n\n","##"," ","4","."," Increase"," the"," pace"," but"," remain"," smooth",".","\n\n","As"," you"," become"," more"," comfortable"," with"," the"," shifting"," motion",","," gradually"," increase"," the"," speed"," while"," maintaining"," smoothness","."," Practice"," this"," repeatedly"," to"," develop"," muscle"," memory"," and"," ensure"," that"," your"," shifts"," are"," seamless",".","\n\n","##"," ","5","."," Place"," your"," left"," hand"," in"," first"," position"," on"," the"," D"," string",".","\n\n","Now",","," place"," your"," left"," hand"," in"," the"," first"," position"," on"," the"," D"," string"," specifically","."," This"," will"," serve"," as"," a"," foundation"," for"," the"," following"," exercises",".","\n\n","##"," ","6","."," Lo","osen"," your"," thumb"," up"," slightly"," and"," move"," your"," hand"," so"," that"," your"," first"," finger"," is"," on"," the"," F","#"," note"," and"," your"," second"," finger"," is"," on"," the"," G"," note",".","\n\n","Relax"," your"," thumb"," and"," slide"," your"," hand"," up"," so"," that"," your"," first"," finger"," lands"," on"," the"," F","#"," note"," and"," your"," second"," finger"," on"," the"," G"," note","."," This"," is"," a"," higher","-","position"," shift"," that"," will"," help"," you"," access"," additional"," notes"," on"," the"," D"," string",".","\n\n","##"," ","7","."," Practice"," lifting"," up"," your"," fingers"," in"," this"," position",".","\n\n","In"," this"," new"," position",","," practice"," lifting"," your"," fingers"," slightly"," above"," the"," strings","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," develop"," control"," and"," accuracy"," in"," this"," higher"," register",".","\n\n","##"," ","8","."," Move"," your"," hand"," back"," to"," first"," position",".","\n\n","Return"," your"," hand"," to"," the"," first"," position"," on"," the"," D"," string","."," Practi","cing"," moving"," back"," and"," forth"," between"," positions"," is"," essential"," to"," improve"," your"," shifting"," technique",".","\n\n","##"," ","9","."," Practice"," moving"," back"," and"," forth"," on"," the"," D"," string",".","\n\n","Repeat"," the"," process"," of"," shifting"," between"," first"," position"," and"," higher"," positions"," on"," the"," D"," string","."," Consistent"," practice"," will"," help"," you"," build"," confidence"," and"," accuracy"," in"," your"," shifts",".","\n\n","##"," ","1","0","."," Place"," your"," left"," hand"," in"," first"," position"," on"," the"," D"," string",".","\n\n","Start"," again"," in"," the"," first"," position"," on"," the"," D"," string","."," Make"," sure"," your"," fingers"," are"," relaxed"," and"," ready"," for"," the"," next"," shift",".","\n\n","##"," ","1","1","."," Press"," down"," all"," your"," fingers"," and"," play",".","\n\n","In"," this"," position",","," press"," down"," all"," your"," fingers"," simultaneously"," and"," play"," a"," note","."," This"," will"," provide"," you"," with"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," finger"," placement"," and"," pressure",".","\n\n","##"," ","1","2","."," Lift"," your"," fingers"," up"," slightly"," and"," move"," back"," to"," first"," position",".","\n\n","Gradu","ally"," lift"," your"," fingers"," and"," return"," to"," the"," first"," position","."," Practi","cing"," this"," movement"," will"," make"," your"," shifts"," smoother"," and"," more"," efficient",".","\n\n","##"," ","1","3","."," Try"," out"," the"," other"," strings",".","\n\n","Apply"," the"," same"," shifting"," techniques"," to"," the"," other"," strings"," (","A",","," G",","," and"," C",")."," This"," will"," help"," you"," become"," versatile"," and"," comfortable"," shifting"," in"," various"," positions"," across"," the"," cello",".","\n\n","##"," ","1","4","."," Practice"," shifting"," to"," the"," various"," positions",".","\n\n","In","corporate"," shifts"," to"," different"," positions"," on"," all"," strings"," in"," your"," practice"," routine","."," This"," wi